Uses of Package
com.eis.greenenergy.help

  • Packages that use com.eis.greenenergy.help 
    Package Description
    com.eis.greenenergy.main
    The activities in this package represent the controller part of the application; they manage and connect the application's view (the layout files) with the application's data model , which is represented by Async-tasks in the package com.eis.greenenergy.connection.
  • Classes in com.eis.greenenergy.help used by com.eis.greenenergy.main 
    Class and Description
    AlertDialogManager
    Auxiliary class to simplify the creation of Alert Dialogs.
    ConnectionDetector
    Auxiliary class to check if the user's internet connection is available.
    PredictionEntry
    An instance of this class represents an entry in the energy prediction list.
    UserManager
    Very important auxiliary class, which manages the user's data, as well as the energy data which is displayed to the user.
